Detailed Description

cvmx_ilk_tx::_mem_cal0

Notes: Software must always read ILK_TXx_MEM_CAL0 then ILK_TXx_MEM_CAL1. Software must never read them in reverse order or read one without reading the other.

Software must always write ILK_TXx_MEM_CAL0 then ILK_TXx_MEM_CAL1. Software must never write them in reverse order or write one without writing the other.
